_sText:
Is cs_office your favorite map? Do you also love jailbreak? Wish the two could combine?

Hello, my name is [blur], and I've made your dreams come true!

Presenting...... jb_office!

This is a jailbreak map I've been working on, based on cs_office. I started with the cs_office map file, and over the past 2 months, I have been working hard to turn it into a jailbreak map for source! jb_office has:

Surf, climb, the floor is lava game, deathchair, musical chairs, breakfloor, courtyard, roof access, soccer, pool, underground minigames area, and more! Throughout the map you'll also find various secrets; some are obvious, some not so much.

Although it's still in beta development, it's mostly done and I've uploaded a stable beta version for playing.

Enjoy!

Special thanks to Gamepunch.net , this map wouldn't have happened without the GP community!
